# Summary
The Settings page in Amplitude allows users to manage both organizational and personal settings, with organization admins controlling features like user permissions, SSO, Session Replay settings (including sample rates and project management), while personal settings include profile management, site preferences, notification controls, and theme selection (light/dark mode).

